        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">```</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">参考文档</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## 从零开始</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">### 安装</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">1. 在`F:\rom新建hexo`目录，右键 `git bash here`</span><br><span class="line">2. 输入`npm install -g hexo-cli`报错 解决办法：搜索c盘用户下.npmrc，删除掉</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![img](https://secure1.wostatic.cn/static/dDR6E2qjs2x7h2n1sBZzrL/image.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">```SQL</span><br><span class="line">npm ERR! code EPERM</span><br><span class="line">npm ERR! syscall open</span><br><span class="line">npm ERR! path C:\Program Files\nodejs\node_cache_cacache\tmp\c3269017</span><br><span class="line">npm ERR! errno EPERM</span><br><span class="line">npm ERR! FetchError: Invalid response body while trying to fetch https://registry.npm.taobao.org/hexo-cli: EPERM: operation not permitted, open &#x27;C:\Program Files\nodejs\node_cache_cacache\tmp\c3269017&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li><code>hexo -v</code>一下，安装成功😺</li></ol><p><img src="https://secure1.wostatic.cn/static/5K2vdFJc29hxK18P9MdRCu/image.png" alt="img"></p><h3 id="初始化"><a href="#初始化" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a>初始化</h3><ol><li><code>hexo init myblog</code>，<code>hexo</code>目录下生成 <a href="F:\rom\hexo"><code>myblog</code></a>文件夹</li></ol><p><img src="https://secure1.wostatic.cn/static/2P2EPD47XJvEJ7KTRszer/image.png" alt="img"></p><ol><li><code>cd myblog</code> //进入这个myblog文件夹 <code>npm install</code></li></ol><p><img src="https://secure1.wostatic.cn/static/wFhyhzFR1R2RdAmYjU8raR/image.png" alt="img"></p><ol><li>hexo g</li><li>启动服务：<code>hexo server</code></li><li>关闭服务：<code>ctrl+C</code></li></ol><p>访问地址：<a href="http://localhost:4000/"><code>localhost:4000</code></a></p><h3 id="GitHub创建个人仓库"><a href="#GitHub创建个人仓库" class="headerlink" title="GitHub创建个人仓库"></a>GitHub创建个人仓库</h3><ol><li>我的github账号：<code>akilleror/z_147258369</code></li><li>创建repository：<a href="http://akilleror.github.io/">akilleror.github.io</a></li><li>回到git bash</li></ol><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config <span class="comment">--global  user.name &quot;akilleror&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git config <span class="comment">--global  user.email &quot;1522569030@qq.com&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建ssh</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh<span class="operator">-</span>keygen <span class="operator">-</span>t rsa <span class="operator">-</span>C &quot;1522569030@qq.com&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在<a href="C:\Users\akiller.ssh"><code>C:\Users\akiller\.ssh</code></a>目录下生成了秘钥</p><ol><li>github录入公钥</li></ol><p><img src="https://secure1.wostatic.cn/static/3awFbhsdpEGGZfQ4WHzVzU/image.png" alt="img"></p><ol><li>校验是否成功</li></ol><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh <span class="operator">-</span>T git<span class="variable">@github</span>.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://secure1.wostatic.cn/static/r6m3dRxE8Pg7Av7u9BmHdF/image.png" alt="img"></p><ol><li>修改<a href="%E2%80%AAF:%5Crom%5Chexo%5Cmyblog_config.yml">_config.yml</a></li></ol><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: https:<span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>github.com<span class="operator">/</span>Akilleror<span class="operator">/</span>Akilleror.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li><code>npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></li><li></li></ol><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br><span class="line">其中 hexo clean清除了你之前生成的东西，也可以不加。</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate 顾名思义，生成静态文章，可以用 hexo g缩写</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy 部署文章，可以用hexo d缩写</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>安装教程内容会报错</li><li><code>Support for password authentication was removed on August 13, 2021. Please use a personal access token instead.</code></li><li>参考文章</li><li>把这个当密码能登进去 :我的令牌<code>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</code></li></ol><p><img src="https://secure1.wostatic.cn/static/6x87HRL8Qhza3Jf14KDa5q/image.png" alt="img"></p><h4 id="访问地址"><a href="#访问地址" class="headerlink" title="访问地址"></a>访问地址</h4><p>、</p><h3 id="hexo基本配置"><a href="#hexo基本配置" class="headerlink" title="hexo基本配置"></a>hexo基本配置</h3><h4 id="写文章"><a href="#写文章" class="headerlink" title="写文章"></a>写文章</h4><p>在<a href="F:\rom\hexo\myblog\source_posts"><code>source/_post</code></a>中打开markdown文件，就可以开始编辑了。当你写完的时候，再</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="报错归档"><a href="#报错归档" class="headerlink" title="报错归档"></a>报错归档</h3><blockquote><p>npm install –save hexo-renderer-jade hexo-generator-feed hexo-generator-sitemap hexo-browsersync hexo-generator-archive</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br><span class="line">或</span><br><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-renderer-jade hexo-generator-feed hexo-generator-sitemap hexo-browsersync hexo-generator-archive</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
